headline: Here is What Lies Ahead For KeyCorp (KEY)
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) is one of the 10 best banking stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On January 26, Truist analyst Brian Foran reaffirmed his Hold rating for KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY).
